    "description": "<strong>Auro The Bunny</strong> 是一款迷人的2D平台游戏，你将控制勇敢的兔子Auro，在各个关卡中收集散落的水果。这项任务需要玩家的极大耐心和精确操作，游戏可能会很快变得黑暗...准备好迎接各种障碍和挑战吧！<br><br><strong>挑战</strong><br>面对众多挑战，它们将考验你的灵活性、反应能力，并很可能考验你的理智...<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1825180/extras/f493e4d4e1fc27a417635c5d7c760acc.poster.avif?t=1737761276\" width=600 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1825180/extras/f493e4d4e1fc27a417635c5d7c760acc.webm?t=1737761276\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1825180/extras/f493e4d4e1fc27a417635c5d7c760acc.mp4?t=1737761276\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><strong>挑战性障碍</strong><br>避开各种危险的障碍物，它们会挡在你的路上。运用智慧克服这些困难。<br><br> <span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1825180/extras/8280644d5a118e315e1f689a87f01d6e.poster.avif?t=1737761276\" width=600 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1825180/extras/8280644d5a118e315e1f689a87f01d6e.webm?t=1737761276\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1825180/extras/8280644d5a118e315e1f689a87f01d6e.mp4?t=1737761276\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><strong>三个独特的场景</strong><br>在不同的环境中探索，和Auro兔子一起面对挑战。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1825180/extras/2ffd0be292d1029450711559bf1f19a5.poster.avif?t=1737761276\" width=600 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1825180/extras/2ffd0be292d1029450711559bf1f19a5.webm?t=1737761276\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1825180/extras/2ffd0be292d1029450711559bf1f19a5.mp4?t=1737761276\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><strong>迷人的原声音乐</strong><br>享受美妙的原声音乐，伴随Auro的旅程。",
